    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Medical)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 5</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The target is healed of fatigue, and if it is suffering from exhaustion, it becomes @Condition[fatigued]{fatigued} instead. In addition, the target is healed of 1d4 temporary ability damage to a single ability score. Using this technique on the same target more than once per day increases the Cost by 2 each time.</p>\n\n\n\n",
